videos.description: Lindell Wigginton drives to the basket and throws down one of the most emphatic dunks of the year.
videos.headline: Wigginton electrifies Iowa State with incredible dunk

videos.description: Iowa State's Lindell Wigginton gets the contact and drills the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Iowa State connects on 3-pointer despite foul

videos.description: Jamuni McNeace bats the missed shot backwards and somehow converts for the bucket.
videos.headline: Oklahoma player tips in shot in without looking

videos.description: Donovan Jackson drills the 3-point shot from the wing despite the contact from Trae Young.
videos.headline: Iowa State knocks down the 3 with the foul

videos.description: Trae Young lobs up the pass to Brady Manek who throws down the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Young's alley-oop to Manek widens gap for Sooners
